---
// Final CTA section - Strong conversion moment
---

<section class="final-cta section-lg" id="download">
  <div class="cta-bg"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content reveal">
      <h2>Stop trying to build habits alone</h2>
      <p>Download TinyAct and pair with someone who'll hold you accountable. When their streak depends on you, showing up becomes automatic.</p>

      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/tinyact" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.81-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/>
          </svg>
          Download Free for iOS
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-meta">
        <div class="cta-meta-item">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>Free forever</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-meta-item">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>No credit card</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-meta-item">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>iOS 15+</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-tagline">
        <span class="tagline-text">"The habit app where quitting doesn't just affect you."</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .final-cta {
    background: var(--bg-dark-gradient);
    color: var(--white);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 50% 0%, rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.25) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 20% 100%, rgba(148, 102, 222, 0.18) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 80% 100%, rgba(87, 199, 96, 0.12) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .cta-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .cta-meta-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .cta-meta-item svg {
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .cta-tagline {
    padding-top: var(--space-8);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .tagline-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cta-content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .cta-content p {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }

    .cta-meta {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-3);
    }
  }
</style>
